item.description: OpenSource Contributions 🌐🖥️ Azure Containerd diskfs: Fix for creating partitions on disk Docker: Fixes related to accessing devices in privileged mode Google Container Tools, Google: Added support for new method in golang github API Kubernetes Kubesphere Moby OpenEBS: Maintainer of OpenEBS disk management plane and local storage options Seagate: Bug fix for NVMe device and memory corruption ⚠️ Sign in to github to view complete list of contributions. Activities (or Talks in the future) 👨🎤 2023 Woman’s mind @ STEP Conference Tech Exhibition Personal Projects 👨 2023 Auth App ▶️ : Authorization with Spring Security.
